  ${
    $d A x y $.  $d B y $.  $d F x y $.  $d G x y $.  $d H x y $.  $d X x y $.
    ghomlin.1 $e |- X = ran G $.
    $( Linearity of a group homomorphism.  (Contributed by Paul Chapman,
       3-Mar-2008.) $)
    ghomlin $p |- ( ( ( G e. GrpOp /\ H e. GrpOp /\ F e. ( G GrpHom H ) ) /\
                      ( A e. X /\ B e. X ) ) ->
                    ( ( F ` A ) H ( F ` B ) ) = ( F ` ( A G B ) ) ) $=
